{
    "publish_date": "2013-10-16T20:20:32.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT10M57S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "I am going to talk to you tonight", 
            "dur": "1.354", 
            "start": "13.395"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about coming out of the closet.", 
            "dur": "1.232", 
            "start": "14.749"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And not in the traditional sense,", 
            "dur": "1.272", 
            "start": "16.487"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not just the &quot;gay&quot; closet.", 
            "dur": "1.697", 
            "start": "17.759"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think we all have closets,", 
            "dur": "1.582", 
            "start": "19.904"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "your closet may be telling someone", 
            "dur": "1.849", 
            "start": "22.233"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you love her for the first time.", 
            "dur": "1.531", 
            "start": "24.082"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or telling someone you&#39;re pregnant.", 
            "dur": "1.705", 
            "start": "25.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or telling someone you have cancer.", 
            "dur": "1.841", 
            "start": "28.144"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or any of the other hard conversations", 
            "dur": "2.491", 
            "start": "30.497"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we have throughout our lives.", 
            "dur": "1.635", 
            "start": "32.988"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All the closet is, \nis a hard conversation.", 
            "dur": "3.649", 
            "start": "34.623"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And although our topics \nmay vary tremendously,", 
            "dur": "2.95", 
            "start": "38.819"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the experience of being in \nand coming out of the closet", 
            "dur": "3.038", 
            "start": "41.769"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is universal.", 
            "dur": "1.46", 
            "start": "44.807"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It is scary, and we hate it,", 
            "dur": "2.615", 
            "start": "46.707"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it needs to be done.", 
            "dur": "1.482", 
            "start": "50.064"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Several years ago, I was working \nat the Southside Walnut Caf\u00e9,", 
            "dur": "3.048", 
            "start": "52.72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.959", 
            "start": "55.768"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a local diner in town,", 
            "dur": "1.834", 
            "start": "57.727"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and during my time there,", 
            "dur": "1.333", 
            "start": "59.561"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would go through phases \nof militant, lesbian, intensity.", 
            "dur": "3.61", 
            "start": "60.894"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.496", 
            "start": "64.504"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not shaving my armpits,", 
            "dur": "1.711", 
            "start": "66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "quoting Ani DiFranco lyrics as gospel,", 
            "dur": "2.734", 
            "start": "67.711"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and depending on the bagginess \nof my cargo shorts,", 
            "dur": "2.4", 
            "start": "71.217"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and how recently I&#39;d shaved my head,", 
            "dur": "2.693", 
            "start": "73.617"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the question would often \nbe sprung on me,", 
            "dur": "1.502", 
            "start": "76.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "usually by a little kid:", 
            "dur": "0.95", 
            "start": "77.812"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Mmmm, are you a boy, \nor are you a girl?&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.438", 
            "start": "80.219"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there would be \nan awkward silence at the table,", 
            "dur": "1.94", 
            "start": "84.969"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;d clench my jaw a little tighter,", 
            "dur": "1.907", 
            "start": "87.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hold my coffee pot \nwith a little more vengeance,", 
            "dur": "2.28", 
            "start": "90.173"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the Dad would awkwardly \nshuffle his newspaper,", 
            "dur": "2.543", 
            "start": "93.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the Mom would shoot \na chilling stare at her kid.", 
            "dur": "2.229", 
            "start": "95.829"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I would say nothing,", 
            "dur": "1.253", 
            "start": "98.501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I would seethe inside.", 
            "dur": "1.798", 
            "start": "100.167"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it got to the point that everytime", 
            "dur": "1.146", 
            "start": "102.403"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I walked up to a table that had a kid", 
            "dur": "1.537", 
            "start": "103.549"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "anywhere between 3 and 10 years old,", 
            "dur": "1.363", 
            "start": "105.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was ready to fight.", 
            "dur": "1.45", 
            "start": "106.449"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.726", 
            "start": "107.899"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that is a terrible feeling.", 
            "dur": "1.79", 
            "start": "109.625"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I promised myself \nthat the next time,", 
            "dur": "1.972", 
            "start": "111.415"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would say something.", 
            "dur": "1.541", 
            "start": "113.387"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would have that hard conversation.", 
            "dur": "1.96", 
            "start": "115.549"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So within a matter of weeks, \nit happens again:", 
            "dur": "2.194", 
            "start": "117.785"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Are you a boy, or are you a girl?&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.549", 
            "start": "119.979"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Familiar silence.", 
            "dur": "1.546", 
            "start": "123.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But this time, I am ready.", 
            "dur": "1.234", 
            "start": "125.025"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I am about to go \nall Woman Studies 101 on this table.", 
            "dur": "4.639", 
            "start": "126.259"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.761", 
            "start": "130.898"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve got my Betty Friedan quotes,", 
            "dur": "2.276", 
            "start": "132.659"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve got my Gloria Steinem quotes,", 
            "dur": "2.041", 
            "start": "134.935"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I even got this little bit from\nVagina Monologues I&#39;m gonna do,", 
            "dur": "2.964", 
            "start": "136.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so I take a deep breath, \nand I look down,", 
            "dur": "2.193", 
            "start": "140.474"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and staring back at me", 
            "dur": "1.469", 
            "start": "143.977"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is a 4-year old girl in a pink dress.", 
            "dur": "2.003", 
            "start": "145.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not a challenge to a feminist duel,", 
            "dur": "2.402", 
            "start": "147.848"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just a kid, with a question:", 
            "dur": "2.002", 
            "start": "150.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Are you a boy, or are you a girl?&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.596", 
            "start": "153.168"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I take another deep breath,", 
            "dur": "1.802", 
            "start": "155.289"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "squat down next to her and say:", 
            "dur": "1.134", 
            "start": "157.091"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Hey, I know it&#39;s kind of confusing,", 
            "dur": "2.369", 
            "start": "158.225"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "my hair is short like a boy&#39;s,", 
            "dur": "1.368", 
            "start": "160.594"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I wear boys&#39; clothes,", 
            "dur": "1.201", 
            "start": "161.962"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I&#39;m a girl", 
            "dur": "1.143", 
            "start": "163.163"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you know how sometimes \nyou like to wear a pink dress,", 
            "dur": "1.927", 
            "start": "164.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and sometimes you like \nto wear your comfie jammies,", 
            "dur": "2.503", 
            "start": "166.233"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "well, I&#39;m more of \na comfie jammies kind of a girl.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "168.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "0.766", 
            "start": "171.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this kid looks me dead in the eye", 
            "dur": "1.966", 
            "start": "172.642"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "without missing a beat and says:", 
            "dur": "0.934", 
            "start": "174.608"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;My favorite pajamas are purple", 
            "dur": "2.036", 
            "start": "175.542"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with fish, can I get a pancake please?&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.102", 
            "start": "177.578"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.712", 
            "start": "179.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that was it, just:", 
            "dur": "1.837", 
            "start": "182.392"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Oh, OK, you&#39;re a girl. \nHow &#39;bout that pancake?&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.205", 
            "start": "184.229"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.121", 
            "start": "187.434"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was the easiest hard conversation \nI have ever had.", 
            "dur": "4.487", 
            "start": "188.555"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And why?", 
            "dur": "1.168", 
            "start": "193.427"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because Pancake Girl and I,", 
            "dur": "1.434", 
            "start": "194.595"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we were both real with each other.", 
            "dur": "1.976", 
            "start": "196.029"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, like many of us,", 
            "dur": "1.841", 
            "start": "199.154"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve lived in a few closets in my life,", 
            "dur": "1.841", 
            "start": "200.995"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and yeah, most often, \nmy walls happen to be rainbow.", 
            "dur": "2.855", 
            "start": "202.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But inside, in the dark,", 
            "dur": "1.629", 
            "start": "206.079"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you can&#39;t tell what color the walls are.", 
            "dur": "2.135", 
            "start": "208.075"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You just know what it feels like", 
            "dur": "1.502", 
            "start": "210.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to live in a closet.", 
            "dur": "1.531", 
            "start": "211.712"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So really, my closet \nis no different than yours,", 
            "dur": "3.012", 
            "start": "213.714"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or yours,", 
            "dur": "1.223", 
            "start": "217.184"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or yours.", 
            "dur": "1.214", 
            "start": "218.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sure, I can give you 100 reasons", 
            "dur": "1.705", 
            "start": "220.522"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "why coming out of my closet", 
            "dur": "0.907", 
            "start": "222.227"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was harder than coming out of yours,", 
            "dur": "1.293", 
            "start": "223.134"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but here&#39;s the thing,", 
            "dur": "0.88", 
            "start": "224.427"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hard is not relative,", 
            "dur": "1.033", 
            "start": "225.307"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hard is hard.", 
            "dur": "1.707", 
            "start": "226.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Who can tell me", 
            "dur": "0.812", 
            "start": "228.765"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that explaining to someone", 
            "dur": "1.645", 
            "start": "229.577"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;ve just declared bankrupcy", 
            "dur": "1.3", 
            "start": "231.222"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is harder than telling someone", 
            "dur": "1.045", 
            "start": "232.522"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when you just cheated on them.", 
            "dur": "1.162", 
            "start": "233.567"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Who can tell me", 
            "dur": "0.908", 
            "start": "234.729"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that his coming out story", 
            "dur": "1.519", 
            "start": "235.793"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is harder than telling your 5-year old", 
            "dur": "1.694", 
            "start": "237.312"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re getting a divorce.", 
            "dur": "1.168", 
            "start": "239.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There is no &quot;harder&quot;,", 
            "dur": "1.101", 
            "start": "240.174"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there is just &quot;hard.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.954", 
            "start": "241.275"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We need to stop ranking our &quot;hard&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.058", 
            "start": "243.788"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "against everybody else&#39;s &quot;hard&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.268", 
            "start": "245.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to make us feel better \nor worse about our closet", 
            "dur": "2.002", 
            "start": "247.114"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and just commiserate on the fact", 
            "dur": "1.468", 
            "start": "249.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that we all have &quot;hard.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.243", 
            "start": "250.584"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At some point in our lives,", 
            "dur": "1.579", 
            "start": "253.587"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we all live in closets,", 
            "dur": "1.718", 
            "start": "255.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they may feel safe.", 
            "dur": "1.41", 
            "start": "256.884"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or at least, safer than what lies", 
            "dur": "1.969", 
            "start": "258.592"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on the other side of that door.", 
            "dur": "1.318", 
            "start": "260.561"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I&#39;m here to tell you,", 
            "dur": "1.186", 
            "start": "262.062"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "no matter what your walls are made of,", 
            "dur": "1.838", 
            "start": "263.764"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a closet is no place \nfor a person to live.", 
            "dur": "3.378", 
            "start": "265.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Cheers)\n(Applause)", 
            "dur": "0.83", 
            "start": "269.907"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thanks.", 
            "dur": "1.302", 
            "start": "270.737"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So why is coming out of any closet,", 
            "dur": "2.301", 
            "start": "274.009"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "why is having that conversation,", 
            "dur": "1.401", 
            "start": "276.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "why is it so hard?", 
            "dur": "1.56", 
            "start": "277.711"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because they&#39;re stressful.", 
            "dur": "1.491", 
            "start": "280.113"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re so concerned about the reaction", 
            "dur": "1.53", 
            "start": "282.287"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of the other person, and understandably.", 
            "dur": "1.829", 
            "start": "283.817"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Will they be angry?", 
            "dur": "1.281", 
            "start": "286.353"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sad?", 
            "dur": "0.679", 
            "start": "287.634"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Disappointed?", 
            "dur": "0.904", 
            "start": "288.313"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Will we loose a friend?", 
            "dur": "0.991", 
            "start": "289.857"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A parent?", 
            "dur": "0.659", 
            "start": "290.848"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A lover?", 
            "dur": "0.819", 
            "start": "291.507"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These conversations cause stress.", 
            "dur": "1.509", 
            "start": "292.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So let&#39;s kick out \non stress for a minute.", 
            "dur": "1.812", 
            "start": "294.628"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Stress is a natural reaction\nin your body.", 
            "dur": "2.539", 
            "start": "296.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you encounter a perceived threat,", 
            "dur": "1.869", 
            "start": "300.033"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-- keyword, &quot;perceived&quot; --", 
            "dur": "1.044", 
            "start": "301.902"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "your hypothalamus sounds the alarm,", 
            "dur": "2.335", 
            "start": "303.237"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and adrenaline and cortisol", 
            "dur": "1.368", 
            "start": "305.572"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "start coursing through your veins.", 
            "dur": "1.957", 
            "start": "306.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is known as", 
            "dur": "1.313", 
            "start": "308.897"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Fight or Flight.", 
            "dur": "2.436", 
            "start": "310.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sometimes you rumble,", 
            "dur": "1.368", 
            "start": "312.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sometimes you run.", 
            "dur": "1.134", 
            "start": "314.014"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this is a totally normal reaction.", 
            "dur": "2.302", 
            "start": "315.148"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And, comes from a time", 
            "dur": "1.739", 
            "start": "317.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when that threat was \nbeing chased by a wooly mammoth.", 
            "dur": "2.942", 
            "start": "319.189"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The problem is", 
            "dur": "1.21", 
            "start": "322.947"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "your hypothalamus has no idea", 
            "dur": "1.737", 
            "start": "324.157"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if you&#39;re being chased \nby a wooly mammoth,", 
            "dur": "2.001", 
            "start": "325.894"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or if your computer just crashed,", 
            "dur": "1.568", 
            "start": "327.895"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or if your in-laws just showed up \non your doorsteps,", 
            "dur": "1.701", 
            "start": "329.463"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or if you&#39;re about \nto jump out of a plane,", 
            "dur": "1.402", 
            "start": "331.164"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or if you need to tell someone you love", 
            "dur": "1.435", 
            "start": "332.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that you have a brain tumor.", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "334.001"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The difference is", 
            "dur": "0.992", 
            "start": "336.273"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the wooly mammoth \nchases you for, what,", 
            "dur": "1.819", 
            "start": "337.838"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "maybe 10 minutes.", 
            "dur": "1.312", 
            "start": "339.657"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not having those hard conversations,", 
            "dur": "1.74", 
            "start": "340.969"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that can go on for years,", 
            "dur": "1.436", 
            "start": "342.709"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and your body just can&#39;t handle that.", 
            "dur": "3.932", 
            "start": "344.145"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Chronic exposure to adrenaline and cortisol", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "348.077"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "disrupts almost every system in your body", 
            "dur": "2.744", 
            "start": "350.717"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and can lead to anxiety,", 
            "dur": "1.643", 
            "start": "353.461"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "depression, heart disease,", 
            "dur": "1.518", 
            "start": "355.104"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just to name a few.", 
            "dur": "1.343", 
            "start": "356.622"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you do not have hard conversations,", 
            "dur": "1.971", 
            "start": "357.965"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when you keep the truth about yourself a secret,", 
            "dur": "2.04", 
            "start": "361.032"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re essentially holding a grenade.", 
            "dur": "2.772", 
            "start": "363.072"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, imagine yourself", 
            "dur": "1.952", 
            "start": "366.715"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "20 years ago.", 
            "dur": "0.895", 
            "start": "369.393"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Me,", 
            "dur": "0.735", 
            "start": "371.004"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had a pony tail,", 
            "dur": "1.715", 
            "start": "372.822"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a strapless dress,", 
            "dur": "1.372", 
            "start": "374.607"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and high heel shoes.", 
            "dur": "1.479", 
            "start": "375.979"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was not the militant lesbian", 
            "dur": "2.051", 
            "start": "377.458"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "ready to fight any 4-year old \nthat walked into the caf\u00e9.", 
            "dur": "2.842", 
            "start": "379.509"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.633", 
            "start": "382.351"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was frozen by fear,", 
            "dur": "1.478", 
            "start": "383.984"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "curled up in a corner", 
            "dur": "1.182", 
            "start": "385.894"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of my pitch-black closet,", 
            "dur": "2.186", 
            "start": "387.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "clutching my gay grenade.", 
            "dur": "1.937", 
            "start": "389.262"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And moving one muscle", 
            "dur": "1.841", 
            "start": "391.658"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is the scariest thing", 
            "dur": "1.663", 
            "start": "393.499"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have ever done.", 
            "dur": "1.822", 
            "start": "395.162"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My family,", 
            "dur": "1.001", 
            "start": "397.965"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "my friends,", 
            "dur": "0.605", 
            "start": "398.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "complete strangers,", 
            "dur": "0.662", 
            "start": "399.571"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had spent my entire life", 
            "dur": "1.369", 
            "start": "400.233"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "trying to not disappoint these people.", 
            "dur": "1.301", 
            "start": "401.602"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And now, I was turning \nthe world upside down.", 
            "dur": "3.155", 
            "start": "402.903"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "On purpose.", 
            "dur": "1.248", 
            "start": "406.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was burning the pages of the script", 
            "dur": "1.763", 
            "start": "408.535"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we had all followed for so long,", 
            "dur": "2.148", 
            "start": "410.298"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but if you do not throw that grenade,", 
            "dur": "1.452", 
            "start": "412.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it will kill you.", 
            "dur": "1.546", 
            "start": "413.898"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One of my most memorable grenade-tosses", 
            "dur": "1.835", 
            "start": "416.483"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was at my sister&#39;s wedding.", 
            "dur": "1.455", 
            "start": "418.318"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "3.263", 
            "start": "419.773"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was the first time \nthat many on attendance", 
            "dur": "1.822", 
            "start": "423.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "knew that I was gay.", 
            "dur": "1.439", 
            "start": "424.858"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So in doing my Maid of Honor duties,", 
            "dur": "1.397", 
            "start": "426.297"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in my black dress and heels,", 
            "dur": "2.347", 
            "start": "427.694"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I walked around the tables,", 
            "dur": "1.141", 
            "start": "430.691"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and finally landed at the table \nof my parents&#39; friends,", 
            "dur": "2.476", 
            "start": "431.832"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "folks that had known me for years.", 
            "dur": "1.668", 
            "start": "434.308"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And after a little small talk,", 
            "dur": "1.91", 
            "start": "436.903"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one of the women shouted out:", 
            "dur": "1.494", 
            "start": "438.813"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;I love Nathan Lane!&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.468", 
            "start": "440.307"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the battle of gay relatebility", 
            "dur": "1.867", 
            "start": "443.178"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "had begun.", 
            "dur": "1.101", 
            "start": "445.045"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Ash, have you ever been to the Castro?&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.702", 
            "start": "446.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Well, yeah, actually, \nwe have friends in San Francisco.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.502", 
            "start": "447.848"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;We&#39;ve never been there,", 
            "dur": "0.968", 
            "start": "450.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but we hear it&#39;s &#39;fa-bu-lous&#39;!!&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.728", 
            "start": "451.318"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Ash, do you know my hairdresser Antonio,", 
            "dur": "1.775", 
            "start": "453.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he&#39;s really good, and \nhe&#39;s never talked about a girlfriend.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "454.821"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Ash, what&#39;s your favorite TV show?", 
            "dur": "1.573", 
            "start": "458.091"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Our favorite TV show: \nfavorite, Will and Grace,", 
            "dur": "2.164", 
            "start": "459.664"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you know who we love? Jack.", 
            "dur": "1.644", 
            "start": "461.828"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Jack is our favorite.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.326", 
            "start": "463.472"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then one woman,", 
            "dur": "1.925", 
            "start": "464.798"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "stumped,", 
            "dur": "1.345", 
            "start": "466.723"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but wanting so desperately\nto show her support,", 
            "dur": "2.235", 
            "start": "468.068"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to let me know she was on my side,", 
            "dur": "2.37", 
            "start": "470.303"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "she finally blurted out:", 
            "dur": "1.368", 
            "start": "472.673"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Well, sometimes my husband \nwears pink shirts.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.67", 
            "start": "474.041"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.873", 
            "start": "477.711"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I had a choice in that moment,", 
            "dur": "1.565", 
            "start": "480.584"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as all grenade-throwers do.", 
            "dur": "1.934", 
            "start": "482.149"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I could go back to my girlfriend,", 
            "dur": "1.568", 
            "start": "484.651"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and my gay-loving table,", 
            "dur": "1.425", 
            "start": "486.219"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and mock their responses.", 
            "dur": "1.906", 
            "start": "487.644"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Chastise their unworldliness,", 
            "dur": "1.548", 
            "start": "490.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and their inability to jump through", 
            "dur": "1.255", 
            "start": "491.638"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the politically-correct gay hoops", 
            "dur": "1.401", 
            "start": "492.893"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had brought with me,", 
            "dur": "1.135", 
            "start": "494.294"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or,", 
            "dur": "0.816", 
            "start": "495.429"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I could empatize with them,", 
            "dur": "1.507", 
            "start": "496.563"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and realize that that was maybe", 
            "dur": "1.396", 
            "start": "498.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one of the hardest things \nthat they had ever done.", 
            "dur": "1.81", 
            "start": "499.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That starting,", 
            "dur": "1.199", 
            "start": "501.802"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and having that conversation,", 
            "dur": "1.597", 
            "start": "503.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was them coming out of their closets.", 
            "dur": "2.168", 
            "start": "505.439"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sure, it would have been easy", 
            "dur": "1.368", 
            "start": "507.607"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to point out where they fell short.", 
            "dur": "1.587", 
            "start": "508.975"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a lot harder", 
            "dur": "1.149", 
            "start": "510.562"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to meet them where they are,", 
            "dur": "1.402", 
            "start": "511.711"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and acknowledge the fact that", 
            "dur": "1.134", 
            "start": "513.113"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they were trying,", 
            "dur": "0.935", 
            "start": "514.247"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and what else can you ask someone to do,", 
            "dur": "2.601", 
            "start": "515.182"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but try.", 
            "dur": "1.477", 
            "start": "517.783"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you&#39;re going to be real with someone,", 
            "dur": "1.781", 
            "start": "520.454"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;ve got to be ready", 
            "dur": "1.308", 
            "start": "522.235"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for real in return.", 
            "dur": "1.648", 
            "start": "523.543"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, hard conversations \nare still not my strong suit.", 
            "dur": "2.769", 
            "start": "526.093"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ask anybody I&#39;ve ever dated.", 
            "dur": "1.906", 
            "start": "528.862"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I&#39;m getting better.", 
            "dur": "1.291", 
            "start": "531.264"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I follow what I like to call", 
            "dur": "1.322", 
            "start": "533.039"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&#39;The Three Pancake Girl Principles.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.568", 
            "start": "534.735"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, please,", 
            "dur": "0.982", 
            "start": "536.303"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "view this through gay-colored lenses,", 
            "dur": "1.851", 
            "start": "538.038"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but know,", 
            "dur": "1.018", 
            "start": "539.889"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what it takes to come out of any closet,", 
            "dur": "1.936", 
            "start": "540.907"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is essentially the same.", 
            "dur": "1.619", 
            "start": "542.843"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Number One:", 
            "dur": "0.833", 
            "start": "545.253"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Be Authentic,", 
            "dur": "1.235", 
            "start": "546.613"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "take the armor off, be yourself.", 
            "dur": "1.397", 
            "start": "547.848"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That kid in the caf\u00e9", 
            "dur": "1.038", 
            "start": "549.245"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "had no armor,", 
            "dur": "1.068", 
            "start": "550.283"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I was ready for battle.", 
            "dur": "1.479", 
            "start": "551.351"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Stupid hypothalamus.", 
            "dur": "1.638", 
            "start": "553.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you want someone to be real with you,", 
            "dur": "2.236", 
            "start": "555.922"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they need to know that you bleed too.", 
            "dur": "2.595", 
            "start": "558.158"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Number Two:", 
            "dur": "0.935", 
            "start": "561.027"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Be Direct,", 
            "dur": "0.734", 
            "start": "561.962"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You say it, rip the bandaid off.", 
            "dur": "1.368", 
            "start": "562.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you know you are gay,", 
            "dur": "1.168", 
            "start": "564.064"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just say it.", 
            "dur": "1.241", 
            "start": "565.232"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you tell your parents \nyou might be gay,", 
            "dur": "1.335", 
            "start": "567.167"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they will hold that hope \nthat this will change.", 
            "dur": "1.564", 
            "start": "568.502"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Do not give them", 
            "dur": "0.871", 
            "start": "570.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that sense of false hope.", 
            "dur": "1.946", 
            "start": "570.937"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.946", 
            "start": "572.883"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And Number Three,", 
            "dur": "1.62", 
            "start": "574.829"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and most important:", 
            "dur": "1.474", 
            "start": "576.449"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "4.326", 
            "start": "577.923"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Be Unapologetic.", 
            "dur": "1.925", 
            "start": "582.249"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You are speaking your truth.", 
            "dur": "1.576", 
            "start": "586.052"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Never apologize for that.", 
            "dur": "2.908", 
            "start": "587.988"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And some folks might \nhave gotten hurt along the way.", 
            "dur": "2.213", 
            "start": "591.825"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So sure.", 
            "dur": "1.057", 
            "start": "594.038"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Apologize for what you&#39;ve done.", 
            "dur": "1.902", 
            "start": "595.095"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But never apologize for who you are.", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "596.997"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And yeah, some folks\nmay be disappointed.", 
            "dur": "1.895", 
            "start": "600.867"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that is on them.", 
            "dur": "1.257", 
            "start": "603.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not on you.", 
            "dur": "1.02", 
            "start": "604.771"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Those are their expectations \nof who you are,", 
            "dur": "1.759", 
            "start": "606.182"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not yours.", 
            "dur": "0.734", 
            "start": "607.941"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That is their story.", 
            "dur": "1.702", 
            "start": "608.675"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not yours.", 
            "dur": "1.792", 
            "start": "610.377"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The only story that matters", 
            "dur": "1.468", 
            "start": "613.213"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is the one that you want to write.", 
            "dur": "1.95", 
            "start": "614.681"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the next time you find yourself", 
            "dur": "2.555", 
            "start": "616.631"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in a pitchblack closet", 
            "dur": "1.334", 
            "start": "619.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "clutching your grenade,", 
            "dur": "1.001", 
            "start": "620.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "know that we&#39;ve all been there before.", 
            "dur": "2.703", 
            "start": "621.521"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you may feel so very alone,", 
            "dur": "2.159", 
            "start": "624.224"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but you are not.", 
            "dur": "0.967", 
            "start": "626.383"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we know it&#39;s hard,", 
            "dur": "1.397", 
            "start": "628.032"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but we need you out here,", 
            "dur": "1.823", 
            "start": "629.429"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "no matter what your walls are made of.", 
            "dur": "2.26", 
            "start": "631.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because I guarantee you", 
            "dur": "1.535", 
            "start": "634.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there are others \npeering through the keyhole", 
            "dur": "1.476", 
            "start": "635.635"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of their closet", 
            "dur": "1.068", 
            "start": "637.111"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "looking for the next brave soul", 
            "dur": "1.231", 
            "start": "638.179"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to bust a door open", 
            "dur": "1.068", 
            "start": "639.41"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so BE that person,", 
            "dur": "1.33", 
            "start": "640.478"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and show the world that \nwe are bigger than our closets,", 
            "dur": "2.095", 
            "start": "642.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that a closet is no place", 
            "dur": "2.039", 
            "start": "645.312"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for a person to truly live.", 
            "dur": "2.946", 
            "start": "647.351"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you Boulder, enjoy your night.", 
            "dur": "1.868", 
            "start": "650.684"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Cheers)\n(Applause)", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "652.552"
        }
    ], 
